casebody.data:
William WIDNER, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
TRAVELERS INSURANCE COMPANY, Defendant,
and
Kinyon Woods Condominiums Association and H & H Lawn Maintenance, Defendants-Appellees. SC: 157534
COA: 339977 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 4, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's September 12, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
